[{"_1":2},"llms/mdx",{"_3":4},"data","# Rewrite Direction (/docs/architecture/rewrite-direction)\n\n\n\nRewrite Direction [#rewrite-direction]\n\nThe rewrite target is a stronger tunnel platform with:\n\n* server-owned tunnel records\n* OIDC-based human authentication\n* separate agent credentials for machine tunnel registration\n* better observability and request logs\n* access controls at ingress\n* WebSocket support\n\nThe current codebase now includes the first persistence foundation:\n\n* SQLite-backed tunnel records\n* persisted request logs\n* stronger client runtime-state cleanup\n"]
